SUMMARY:Narita Airport (NRT)
DESCRIPTION:Land at NRT Terminal 1 (or 2). Customs + baggage claim typically 30-60 min for international arrivals. After clearing\, drop checked bags at the Yamato Transport (Kuroneko Takkyubin) counter in Arrivals — next-day delivery to Yuen Shinjuku at ~¥2\,500-3\,500/bag. Then proceed to the rail station beneath the terminal.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Narita%20Airport%20(NRT)%2C%2035.76479%2C140.38583
LOCATION:Narita International Airport Terminal 1\, Narita\, Chiba 282-0004
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Narita%20Airport%20(NRT)%2C%2035.76479%2C140.38583
GEO:35.76479;140.38583
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:japan-honeymoon-2025-d1-1c@trip-atlas
DTSTAMP:20260715T020241Z
DTSTART:20261124T083000Z
DTEND:20261124T095500Z
SUMMARY:NRT Airport Station — board N'EX
DESCRIPTION:After customs (~30-60 min) + Yamato luggage drop at the Arrivals counter\, head down to the rail level beneath Terminal 1 (~5 min walk from arrivals). **Take the JR Narita Express (N'EX) bound for Shinjuku** — departs roughly every 30 min. ~85 min ride\, all-reserved seats (¥3\,250pp ordinary). Board the front 6 cars (split at Tokyo Station). Buy ticket at the JR ticket office in Arrivals or via JR East online reservation.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=NRT%20Airport%20Station%20%E2%80%94%20board%20N'EX%2C%2035.76479%2C140.38583
LOCATION:Narita Airport Station (under Terminal 1)\, Narita\, Chiba
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=NRT%20Airport%20Station%20%E2%80%94%20board%20N'EX%2C%2035.76479%2C140.38583
GEO:35.76479;140.38583
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:japan-honeymoon-2025-d1-1d@trip-atlas
DTSTAMP:20260715T020241Z
DTSTART:20261124T100000Z
DTEND:20261124T102500Z
SUMMARY:Shinjuku JR Station — exit East
DESCRIPTION:N'EX terminates at Shinjuku JR Station. Use the East Exit for taxi rank. Short taxi (~5 min\, ¥1\,000) gets you to Yuen — easier than rolling carry-on through the Marunouchi Line transfer to Shinjuku-Gyoemmae\, even though Yuen is only 1km away.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Shinjuku%20JR%20Station%20%E2%80%94%20exit%20East%2C%2035.6896%2C139.7006
LOCATION:Shinjuku Station\, 3-38-1 Shinjuku\, Shinjuku-ku\, Tokyo
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Shinjuku%20JR%20Station%20%E2%80%94%20exit%20East%2C%2035.6896%2C139.7006
GEO:35.6896;139.7006
END:VEVENT
