DTEND:20261124T112500Z
SUMMARY:Onsen Ryokan Yuen Shinjuku check-in
DESCRIPTION:~5 min taxi from Shinjuku JR East Exit (~¥1\,000) or 15 min walk if you want to stretch. Drop bags\, freshen up\, soak the jet lag away in the 18F rooftop open-air onsen before late dinner.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Onsen%20Ryokan%20Yuen%20Shinjuku%20check-in%2C%2035.69156%2C139.70908
LOCATION:5-3-18 Shinjuku\, Shinjuku Ward\, Tokyo 160-0022
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Onsen%20Ryokan%20Yuen%20Shinjuku%20check-in%2C%2035.69156%2C139.70908
GEO:35.69156;139.70908
END:VEVENT
