DTEND:20261124T123000Z
SUMMARY:Afuri Shinjuku Lumine1
DESCRIPTION:Same exact Afuri yuzu-shio ramen experience as the Harajuku original — light\, clean\, citrus-forward Tokyo first-night classic. Lumine1 B2F at Shinjuku Station (open till 22:00\, so 20:30 is the late-arrival sweet spot). 1 stop on the Marunouchi Line from Yuen\, or a 20-min walk west through Shinjuku 3-chome.\n~1500 JPY pp\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Afuri%20Shinjuku%20Lumine1%2C%2035.68855%2C139.70016
LOCATION:Lumine1 B2F\, 1-1-5 Nishi-Shinjuku\, Shinjuku-ku\, Tokyo
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Afuri%20Shinjuku%20Lumine1%2C%2035.68855%2C139.70016
GEO:35.68855;139.70016
END:VEVENT
