SUMMARY:Senso-ji Temple
DESCRIPTION:Tokyo's oldest temple\, 7th century. Walk under Kaminarimon lantern. Early arrival = fewer tour buses.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Senso-ji%20Temple%2C%2035.7148%2C139.7967
LOCATION:35.7148\,139.7967
