SUMMARY:Kappabashi Kitchen Town — browse
DESCRIPTION:10-min walk N from Nakamise end. 800m of kitchen-supply shops — knives\, ceramics\, lifelike plastic food samples\, kitchenware. **Browse only — defer real knife purchase to Kyoto Aritsugu (Nishiki Market Day 8) or Sugimoto/Tsubaya (Tsukiji Day 15) where the experience is more authentic + less touristy.** Even just walking the strip is a Tokyo curiosity. ~45 min plenty.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Kappabashi%20Kitchen%20Town%20%E2%80%94%20browse%2C%2035.7148%2C139.7891
LOCATION:Kappabashi-dori\, Matsugaya\, Taito-ku\, Tokyo
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Kappabashi%20Kitchen%20Town%20%E2%80%94%20browse%2C%2035.7148%2C139.7891
GEO:35.7148;139.7891
END:VEVENT
