DTSTART:20261125T040000Z
DTEND:20261125T042500Z
SUMMARY:Walk to Ueno Park
DESCRIPTION:~15-20 min walk W along Asakusa-dori (or through Kappabashi continuing N). Enters Ueno Park from the NE side. Bathrooms at Tokyo National Museum if needed.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Walk%20to%20Ueno%20Park%2C%2035.7148%2C139.7745
LOCATION:Ueno Park entrance\, Taito-ku\, Tokyo
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Walk%20to%20Ueno%20Park%2C%2035.7148%2C139.7745
GEO:35.7148;139.7745
END:VEVENT
