DESCRIPTION:Quick Marunouchi Line ride from Shinjuku-Gyoemmae to Yoyogi-Koen — relaxed morning walk through cedars + autumn leaves before catching the 10:30 Fuji Excursion. Last Tokyo activity before heading to the lake.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Yoyogi%20Park%20walk%2C%2035.6716%2C139.6948
