SUMMARY:Meiji Jingu Shrine
DESCRIPTION:Major Shinto shrine in a vast forested grove — the counterpart to Senso-ji's Buddhist scale. Quiet at this hour\, you'll have the gravel paths almost to yourselves. Allow ~90 min round trip from main torii.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Meiji%20Jingu%20Shrine%2C%2035.6764%2C139.6993
LOCATION:1-1 Yoyogi Kamizonocho\, Shibuya City
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Meiji%20Jingu%20Shrine%2C%2035.6764%2C139.6993
GEO:35.6764;139.6993
END:VEVENT
