SUMMARY:Shinjuku Station — bento + coffee
DESCRIPTION:~15 min from Meiji Jingu: walk south to Harajuku Station\, JR Yamanote 1 stop to Shinjuku. Grab an ekiben from Ecute Shinjuku or the Lumine bakery — Fuji Excursion boards at ~10:25.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Shinjuku%20Station%20%E2%80%94%20bento%20%2B%20coffee%2C%2035.6896%2C139.7006
