DTEND:20261127T032500Z
SUMMARY:Fuji Excursion — board at Shinjuku
DESCRIPTION:**JR/Fujikyu Limited Express "Fuji Excursion No. 11"** — 10:30 departure from Shinjuku Platform 9/10. ~1h55m direct\, arrives Kawaguchiko 12:25\, ¥4\,200pp all-reserved (no non-reserved cars). **CRITICAL: Book exactly one month in advance at 10:00 a.m. JST** (set Oct 27 calendar reminder). Watch for Mt Fuji views on the RIGHT side of the train after Otsuki.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Fuji%20Excursion%20%E2%80%94%20board%20at%20Shinjuku%2C%2035.6896%2C139.7006
LOCATION:35.6896\,139.7006
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Fuji%20Excursion%20%E2%80%94%20board%20at%20Shinjuku%2C%2035.6896%2C139.7006
GEO:35.6896;139.7006
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:japan-honeymoon-2025-d4-4@trip-atlas
DTSTAMP:20260715T020241Z
DTSTART:20261127T033000Z
DTEND:20261127T035500Z
SUMMARY:Kawaguchiko Station
DESCRIPTION:Arrive Kawaguchiko Station 12:30. Phone Ubuya on +81-555-72-1145 — their on-call shuttle runs 14:30-18:00 (~10 min\, free). Since you're arriving before 14:30\, options: (a) wait ~30 min for shuttle window\, (b) taxi (~¥2\,000\, 10 min) for fastest\, (c) Red Line sightseeing bus to 'Kozantei Ubuya' stop (~16 min\, ¥420). All three are fine — taxi is cleanest with even a small bag.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Kawaguchiko%20Station%2C%2035.49833%2C138.76861
LOCATION:35.49833\,138.76861
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Kawaguchiko%20Station%2C%2035.49833%2C138.76861
GEO:35.49833;138.76861
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:japan-honeymoon-2025-d4-5@trip-atlas
DTSTAMP:20260715T020241Z
DTSTART:20261127T040000Z
DTEND:20261127T042500Z
SUMMARY:Ubuya bag drop + lobby lounge
DESCRIPTION:Standard ryokan check-in is 15:00 — too early to actually check in\, but front desk will hold bags and you can use the lake-view lobby. Getting there: phone +81-555-72-1145 for the on-call shuttle (runs 14:30-18:00\, so won't help yet)\, taxi (~¥2\,000\, 10 min\, fastest)\, or Red Line bus to 'Kozantei Ubuya' stop (~16 min\, ¥420). Taxi is cleanest with bags.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Ubuya%20bag%20drop%20%2B%20lobby%20lounge%2C%2035.5128155%2C138.7688497
LOCATION:35.5128155\,138.7688497
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Ubuya%20bag%20drop%20%2B%20lobby%20lounge%2C%2035.5128155%2C138.7688497
GEO:35.5128155;138.7688497
END:VEVENT
