UID:japan-honeymoon-2025-d4-5b@trip-atlas
DTSTAMP:20260715T020241Z
DTSTART:20261127T043000Z
DTEND:20261127T055500Z
SUMMARY:Lake Kawaguchi cape walk + lunch
DESCRIPTION:Bags stowed — wander the Ubuyazaki cape promontory\, grab a casual lunch nearby (the area around Ubuya has a few cafes + soba spots)\, or just sit lakeside with Mt Fuji in view. Houtou Fudou north shore is a 10-min taxi if you want the iconic noodle hot pot now instead of Day 5 (would need to swap).\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Lake%20Kawaguchi%20cape%20walk%20%2B%20lunch%2C%2035.5128%2C138.77
LOCATION:35.5128\,138.77
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Lake%20Kawaguchi%20cape%20walk%20%2B%20lunch%2C%2035.5128%2C138.77
GEO:35.5128;138.77
END:VEVENT
