DTSTART:20261127T060000Z
DTEND:20261127T080000Z
SUMMARY:Kozantei Ubuya check-in
DESCRIPTION:Official check-in at 15:00 — yukata fitting\, room tour\, onsen orientation. ~3.5 hours before Kaiseki #1 = perfect window for a first onsen soak + unwind from the travel day.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Kozantei%20Ubuya%20check-in%2C%2035.5128155%2C138.7688497
