SUMMARY:Houtou Fudou lunch
DESCRIPTION:Iconic Yamanashi noodle hot pot in a rustic folk-art farmhouse — wide flat noodles + vegetables in miso broth\, served in a cast-iron pot the size of a small wheel. North shore\, 5-10 min taxi from Ubuya\, opens 11:00. Kicks off the active afternoon loop.\n~1500 JPY pp\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Houtou%20Fudou%20lunch%2C%2035.518%2C138.7472
LOCATION:707 Kawaguchi\, Fujikawaguchiko-machi\, Minamitsuru-gun\, Yamanashi 401-0304
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Houtou%20Fudou%20lunch%2C%2035.518%2C138.7472
GEO:35.518;138.7472
END:VEVENT
