DTSTART:20261128T050000Z
DTEND:20261128T062500Z
SUMMARY:Oshino Hakkai
DESCRIPTION:Eight crystalline spring ponds fed by Mt Fuji snowmelt\, surrounded by a preserved Edo-era village. Walking the loop takes ~90 min. Try the trout from the pond water + the local manju sweet at the shops near the entrance.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Oshino%20Hakkai%2C%2035.46003%2C138.83289
LOCATION:Oshino-mura\, Minamitsuru-gun\, Yamanashi 401-0511
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Oshino%20Hakkai%2C%2035.46003%2C138.83289
GEO:35.46003;138.83289
END:VEVENT
