DTSTART:20261128T063000Z
DTEND:20261128T075500Z
SUMMARY:Mt Fuji Panoramic Ropeway
DESCRIPTION:Gondola from the south shore of Lake Kawaguchi up Mt Tenjo — Mt Fuji panorama from ~1100m. Round trip ¥1\,000pp\, ~3 min each way. Quick scenic stop before heading back to Ubuya for the lake walk + last kaiseki.\n~1000 JPY pp\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Mt%20Fuji%20Panoramic%20Ropeway%2C%2035.50381%2C138.77419
LOCATION:1163 Azagawa\, Fujikawaguchiko-machi\, Minamitsuru-gun\, Yamanashi 401-0303
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Mt%20Fuji%20Panoramic%20Ropeway%2C%2035.50381%2C138.77419
GEO:35.50381;138.77419
END:VEVENT
