DTSTAMP:20260715T020241Z
DTSTART:20261128T080000Z
DTEND:20261128T092500Z
SUMMARY:Lake Kawaguchi north shore walk
DESCRIPTION:Easy walk back along the lake at Ubuya area — sunset over Mt Fuji from the cape\, decompress from the active afternoon before kaiseki. Optional\, can swap for last onsen if you're wiped.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Lake%20Kawaguchi%20north%20shore%20walk%2C%2035.5182%2C138.7605
LOCATION:35.5182\,138.7605
