DTEND:20261128T103000Z
SUMMARY:Kaiseki dinner #2 · hanafuda night
DESCRIPTION:Multi-course dinner at the ryokan. Bring the Nintendo hanafuda deck picked up Day 3 and learn Koi-Koi over sake — watch a quick rules video on the way to dinner. Quiet lake\, paper screens\, two-player game.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Kaiseki%20dinner%20%232%20%C2%B7%20hanafuda%20night%2C%2035.5128155%2C138.7688497
LOCATION:35.5128155\,138.7688497
