DTEND:20261129T002500Z
SUMMARY:Japanese breakfast at the ryokan
DESCRIPTION:Final Ubuya breakfast — leisurely\, no rush since the active stuff was yesterday. Last morning onsen after.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Japanese%20breakfast%20at%20the%20ryokan%2C%2035.5128155%2C138.7688497
LOCATION:35.5128155\,138.7688497
