DTEND:20261129T015500Z
SUMMARY:Last morning onsen at Ubuya
DESCRIPTION:Final dip with the Mt Fuji + lake view before checkout. Pack between sessions.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Last%20morning%20onsen%20at%20Ubuya%2C%2035.5128155%2C138.7688497
LOCATION:35.5128155\,138.7688497
