DTSTART:20261129T020000Z
DTEND:20261129T025500Z
SUMMARY:Ubuya checkout
DESCRIPTION:Standard ryokan checkout is 11:00. Taxi or short drive ~5 min to FUFU. Email FUFU ahead (reservation1@fufukawaguchiko.jp) requesting early check-in around 12:00 — they typically accommodate splurge-tier guests with confirmed dinner reservations.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Ubuya%20checkout%2C%2035.5128155%2C138.7688497
LOCATION:35.5128155\,138.7688497
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Ubuya%20checkout%2C%2035.5128155%2C138.7688497
