DTSTAMP:20260715T020241Z
DTSTART:20261129T030000Z
DTEND:20261129T045500Z
SUMMARY:Arrive FUFU Kawaguchiko
DESCRIPTION:Drop bags at FUFU. If suite isn't ready yet\, use the lobby lounge\, garden\, or grab a light lunch / matcha at the on-site cafe. Aim for room ready by 14:00 (if early check-in arranged) or 15:00 standard.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Arrive%20FUFU%20Kawaguchiko%2C%2035.5282327%2C138.7599385
LOCATION:35.5282327\,138.7599385
