DTSTAMP:20260715T020241Z
DTSTART:20261129T050000Z
DTEND:20261129T065500Z
SUMMARY:Settle into FUFU suite + first private onsen
DESCRIPTION:Once your suite is ready: unpack\, put on the yukata\, fire up the private outdoor onsen overlooking Mt Fuji. The whole point of paying for FUFU.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Settle%20into%20FUFU%20suite%20%2B%20first%20private%20onsen%2C%2035.5282327%2C138.7599385
