DTSTAMP:20260715T020241Z
DTSTART:20261129T070000Z
DTEND:20261129T090000Z
SUMMARY:Couples massage at FUFU (in-suite)
DESCRIPTION:In-suite couples massage by FUFU therapist — 50 or 90 min. Email reservation1@fufukawaguchiko.jp ~1 week ahead to book the simultaneous-couples slot (your specific suite type needs to support two therapists\; confirm when reserving). 50 min ¥7\,950pp · 90 min ¥13\,250pp. Service hours 10:00-19:00. Perfect afternoon-into-kaiseki transition with the rooftop views and the private onsen for a soak afterward.\n~13250 JPY pp\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Couples%20massage%20at%20FUFU%20(in-suite)%2C%2035.5282327%2C138.7599385
LOCATION:35.5282327\,138.7599385
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Couples%20massage%20at%20FUFU%20(in-suite)%2C%2035.5282327%2C138.7599385
GEO:35.5282327;138.7599385
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:japan-honeymoon-2025-d6-6@trip-atlas
DTSTAMP:20260715T020241Z
DTSTART:20261129T093000Z
