DESCRIPTION:Fujikyu/JR Bus limited express to Mishima Station\, ~95 min\, ¥2\,250pp. Reservations recommended on highway-buses.jp but walk-ups boardable if seats free. Arrives Mishima South Exit\, right at the Tokaido Shinkansen platforms.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Mishima-Kawaguchiko%20Liner%20%E2%80%94%20board%20at%20Kawaguchiko%20Station%2C%2035.49833%2C138.76861
