SUMMARY:Mishima Station
DESCRIPTION:**Target a Mishima-STOPPING Hikari Shinkansen — NOT Kodama\, NOT Nozomi.** Nozomi never stops at Mishima. Only some Hikari trains stop here. Mishima-stopping Hikari takes ~1h50-2h to Kyoto (~110-115min). Kodama takes ~2h45m (avoid). **Book in advance via JR East SmartEX app or station midori-no-madoguchi** before traveling — show up at Mishima with a confirmed Hikari ticket\, do NOT board the next westbound train blindly. Sit D-side (right facing forward) for Mt Fuji views in the first ~20min after Mishima.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Mishima%20Station%2C%2035.1281%2C138.9117
LOCATION:35.1281\,138.9117
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Mishima%20Station%2C%2035.1281%2C138.9117
GEO:35.1281;138.9117
