SUMMARY:Hisago oyakodon
DESCRIPTION:Chicken + egg over rice.\n\n**BACKUP LUNCH OPTIONS** if Hisago line is brutal (60-90min waits common):\n- **Okutan Kiyomizu** — oldest yudofu in Kyoto (1635)\, Sannenzaka/Ninenzaka intersection. ¥3\,000 set.\n- **Akoya Chaya** (Ninenzaka) — ochazuke buffet with 20+ pickles. Cheap\, fast — best bailout.\n- **Omen Kodaiji** — fat udon dipping noodles\, locals + Anthony Bourdain favorite.\n- **Higashiyama Yuuzu** — Miyama yuba workshop restaurant\, locals' yuba pick.\n- **Junsei Okabe-ya** — tofu + yuba kaiseki right at Kiyomizu base\, garden seating.\n~1500 JPY pp\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Hisago%20oyakodon%2C%2035.0033%2C135.78
LOCATION:484 Shimokawaracho\, Higashiyama-ku\, Kyoto
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Hisago%20oyakodon%2C%2035.0033%2C135.78
GEO:35.0033;135.78
