SUMMARY:Nakamura Tokichi Honten
DESCRIPTION:Matcha soba + parfait.\n\n**UJI MATCHA BACKUP OPTIONS** if Nakamura line is brutal:\n- **Itohkyuemon Uji Honten** — matcha soba + matcha desserts\, best fallback.\n- **Tsuen Tea** — founded 1160\, oldest tea shop in Japan. By Uji Bridge — served Hideyoshi.\n- **Masuda Chaho** — front gate of Byodo-in. Freshly stone-ground matcha on ice cream. **Locals' pick over Nakamura.**\n- **Fukujuen Uji-cha Kobo** — workshop where you grind your own matcha.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Nakamura%20Tokichi%20Honten%2C%2034.8907%2C135.8079
LOCATION:34.8907\,135.8079
