SUMMARY:Fushimi Inari Taisha · sunrise hike
DESCRIPTION:Timing is everything — at 7 AM the 10K torii path is nearly empty\, mystical light\, photographers only. Hike to the Yotsutsuji intersection viewpoint (~45 min up\, 30 min down). Skip the summit if tired — Yotsutsuji is where the view opens. Free\, 24/7.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Fushimi%20Inari%20Taisha%20%C2%B7%20sunrise%20hike%2C%2034.967%2C135.7728
LOCATION:34.967\,135.7728
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Fushimi%20Inari%20Taisha%20%C2%B7%20sunrise%20hike%2C%2034.967%2C135.7728
GEO:34.967;135.7728
END:VEVENT
