DTEND:20261204T062500Z
SUMMARY:Takoyaki Wanaka
DESCRIPTION:¥600 for 8.\n\n**BONUS DOTONBORI CRAWL PICKS** beyond your 6 planned anchors:\n\n**OTHER TAKOYAKI**\n- **Otako** — oldest takoyaki in Dotonbori\, larger octopus chunks (locals').\n- **Takoya Dotonbori Kukuru** — softer/creamier interior\, giant octopus signboard\, eat-in upstairs.\n- **Konamon Museum (Dotonbori)** — 5-brand takoyaki sampler under one roof (Aizuya + Kukuru + Juhachiban + Yamachan + Kogaryu).\n\n**ALT OKONOMIYAKI**\n- **Hozenji Sanpei** ⭐ — Time Out Osaka #1 pick\, 40+ years\, tiny counter inside Hozenji Yokocho (overlaps your anchor).\n- **Chibo Dotonbori** — big chain\, reliable\, less touristy than Mizuno.\n- **Negiyaki Yamamoto** (Namba branch) — green-onion pancake\, locals' niche pick.\n\n**CRAB / SUSHI / ICONIC**\n- **Kani Doraku Honten** — giant moving crab sign\; streetside stall has grilled crab legs + crab shumai.\n- **Kura Sushi Dotonbori** — ¥115/plate conveyor belt\, gacha-prize gimmick.\n\n**PORK BUNS / RAMEN / LATE-NIGHT**\n- **551 Horai Namba/Dotonbori** ⭐ — Osaka butaman (pork buns) since 1945\; red box is THE Osaka souvenir. Steam-grab-and-go.\n- **Ichiran Dotonbori Main Building** — 24-hour tonkotsu\, the flagship destination branch.\n\n**DESSERT / PHOTO**\n- **Pablo Cheese Tart** (Shinsaibashi 1-chome flagship) — founding location\, freshly baked half-baked tart.\n- **Strawberry Mania Dotonbori** — strawberry tanghulu (crystal-glazed skewer\, ¥600).\n- **Rikuro's Cheesecake Namba Honten** — jiggly cheesecake from the oven with branded bell ring\, 5 min south.\n~600 JPY pp\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Takoyaki%20Wanaka%2C%2034.6657%2C135.5031
LOCATION:34.6657\,135.5031
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Takoyaki%20Wanaka%2C%2034.6657%2C135.5031
GEO:34.6657;135.5031
END:VEVENT
