DESCRIPTION:Castle keep + museum + park grounds. Fall foliage peaks late November — momiji + ginkgo around the moats. Grab a quick lunch inside the park (food carts) or at Jo-Terrace Osaka before climbing to the observation deck.\n~600 JPY pp\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Osaka%20Castle%20Park%2C%2034.6873%2C135.5258
