DTSTAMP:20260715T020241Z
DTSTART:20261205T100000Z
DTEND:20261205T120000Z
SUMMARY:Kushikatsu Daruma Shinsekai
DESCRIPTION:Original location.\n\n**Note:** You already did the Daruma chain on Day 11 Dotonbori. Consider **Yaekatsu** instead (locals' #1\, 70+ years\, just up the alley) for a different operator. Daruma Shinsekai Honten is 1929 original if you want the chain heritage.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Kushikatsu%20Daruma%20Shinsekai%2C%2034.6518%2C135.5063
LOCATION:34.6518\,135.5063
