SUMMARY:Bar Nayuta · speakeasy
DESCRIPTION:Dotonbori-area speakeasy. Hidden door\, classic + creative cocktails\, intimate bar. Walk 15 min back from Shinsekai to Namba. Cocktails ¥1500–2500. Cash preferred.\n~4000 JPY pp\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Bar%20Nayuta%20%C2%B7%20speakeasy%2C%2034.672034%2C135.498379
