SUMMARY:Shin-Osaka Station — board Nozomi
DESCRIPTION:Subway from Namba to Shin-Osaka (~15 min on Midosuji Line). **Take any Nozomi bound for Tokyo** — every ~10 min\, ~2h22-2h27 direct\, ¥13\,720pp ordinary reserved. **Sit D seat in a standard car (right side facing forward)** for ~30 min of Mt Fuji views on a clear day after Maibara. The Yamato bags meet you at Shibuya REI by evening.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Shin-Osaka%20Station%20%E2%80%94%20board%20Nozomi%2C%2034.73319%2C135.50034
