SUMMARY:Bar Benfiddich · nightcap
DESCRIPTION:Hiroyasu Kayama's apothecary cocktail bar — World's 50 Best #18 (2025)\, Asia's top cocktail destination. He farms his own herbs in Chichibu\, prepares drinks with mortar + pestle at the 17-seat counter. Absinthe specialist with original macerations. 5-min walk from Hyatt Regency back to hotel after. ⚠️ Reservations MANDATORY in 2025 — book via Tablecheck day-before 3-6pm Japan time\, or BEFORE you fly via concierge. Closed Sundays (Dec 7 = Sat OK\, Dec 8 = Sun OUT if scheduling on the wrong night). Walk-ins essentially impossible.\n~6000 JPY pp\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Bar%20Benfiddich%20%C2%B7%20nightcap%2C%2035.6929%2C139.6953
LOCATION:9F\, 1-13-7 Nishi-Shinjuku\, Shinjuku-ku\, Tokyo
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Bar%20Benfiddich%20%C2%B7%20nightcap%2C%2035.6929%2C139.6953
GEO:35.6929;139.6953
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
