SUMMARY:Cat Street vintage cluster (Harajuku)
DESCRIPTION:Better fit-odds than Shimokita for tall/broader bodies — these are US-sourced. Walk Cat Street + side alleys: 2nd Street (consistent sizing)\, BerBerJin (Western Levi's including bigger waists)\, Komehyo Harajuku (used designer\, accurate sizing)\, Atlantis Vintage (US/EU vintage). Skip Kinji/Pin Nap (small Japanese-only sizing).\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Cat%20Street%20vintage%20cluster%20(Harajuku)%2C%2035.6692%2C139.7068
