SUMMARY:Hotel checkout + bag claim ticket at concierge
DESCRIPTION:Check out 07:30\, leave bags at front desk. Buy your Limousine Bus ticket the night before at the concierge (¥1\,400pp) — they'll tell you the departure time + curbside loading spot. Bring bags to lobby 10 min before bus departure\; concierge directs you to the loading curb\, driver tags + loads bags under the bus.\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Hotel%20checkout%20%2B%20bag%20claim%20ticket%20at%20concierge%2C%2035.6912457%2C139.69126
