DTEND:20261208T235500Z
SUMMARY:Airport Limousine Bus to Haneda
DESCRIPTION:¥1\,400 per person\, ~50 min to HND Terminal 3 (international). Driver tags your bag with destination label\, loads it under the bus — you get a claim ticket. Hand the ticket to driver at HND to retrieve. Buses use the Shuto Expressway bus lane so they often beat taxis in rush hour. First HND-bound bus ~5:30 AM\, frequent service until evening. Reservation recommended via limousinebus.co.jp/en or front desk.\n~1400 JPY pp\nhttps://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Airport%20Limousine%20Bus%20to%20Haneda%2C%2035.6912457%2C139.69126
LOCATION:Hyatt Regency Tokyo main entrance\, 2-7-2 Nishi-Shinjuku
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Airport%20Limousine%20Bus%20to%20Haneda%2C%2035.6912457%2C139.69126
GEO:35.6912457;139.69126
END:VEVENT
