SUMMARY:Hotel · Onsen Ryokan Yuen Shinjuku
DESCRIPTION:✅ BOOKED via Chase Travel Portal (5x CSP points earn). Confirmation #: 2507657067. Primary guest: MADISON R FRAITAG. Room: Small Double\, Non-Smoking. Total: US$769.96 for 3 nights ($256.65/night). Free cancellation until Sun Nov 22\, 2026 11:59 pm property local time. Modern ryokan with 18F open-air rooftop onsen overlooking Tokyo skyline. Quiet east-Shinjuku block\, 5 min from Shinjuku-Gyoemmae Metro. Yukatas + traditional Japanese breakfast included.
