SUMMARY:Hotel · FUFU Kawaguchiko
DESCRIPTION:✅ BOOKED via Agoda. Guest: Brian Heubel (brianheubel@gmail.com). Room: Konohana Comfort Suite\, 1 room. GRAND TOTAL: US$1\,264.48. Free cancellation until ~Sep 29\, 2026 — TAKE ADVANTAGE if the itinerary shifts. ⚠️ Booking likely BREAKFAST ONLY (kaiseki dinner was sold out on FUFU direct at booking time). To add kaiseki: email reservation1@fufukawaguchiko.jp with Agoda confirmation + request in-room kaiseki add-on (~¥15-25K/pp extra). Splurge final Fuji night — all-suite property\, private outdoor onsen per room\, Mt Fuji views\, Bang & Olufsen\, Dyson.
