SUMMARY:Hotel · Apartment Hotel 11 Yasaka
DESCRIPTION:✅ BOOKED via Booking.com. 4 nights\, $589.19 total ($147/night — massive $311 off retail via Early Booker -$162 + Genius Discount -$90 + Booking.com credit -$59). ¥95\,428 in property currency. Apartment-style hotel in Higashiyama's temple heart — 5 min walk to Yasaka Shrine\, 14 min uphill to Kiyomizu via Sannenzaka/Ninenzaka\, 10 min to Gion-Shijo Keihan Station. Day 8 (Kimono + Higashiyama walk) is entirely on foot from here. Check-in from 4pm\, check-out by 10am. ⚠️ Before arrival: verify daily housekeeping\, request higher floor to avoid Higashi-oji road noise\, confirm private ensuite bathroom.
LOCATION:487 Shimokawaracho\, Higashiyama Ward\, Kyoto 605-0825
URL:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Apartment%20Hotel%2011%20Yasaka%2C%2035%2C135.7793
